#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.copy.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.copy"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.core.Series.copy:1 of
msgid "Make a copy of this object's indices and data."
msgstr "复制此对象的索引和数据。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.core.Series.copy:3 of
msgid ""
"When ``deep=True`` (default), a new object will be created with a copy of"
" the calling object's data and indices. Modifications to the data or "
"indices of the copy will not be reflected in the original object (see "
"notes below)."
msgstr ""
"当 ``deep=True``（默认）时，将创建一个新对象，其中包含调用对象的数据和"
"索引的副本。对副本的数据或索引的修改不会反映在原始对象中（请参见以下说明"
"）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.core.Series.copy:8 of
msgid ""
"When ``deep=False``, a new object will be created without copying the "
"calling object's data or index (only references to the data and index are"
" copied). Any changes to the data of the original will be reflected in "
"the shallow copy (and vice versa)."
msgstr ""
"当 ``deep=False`` 时，将创建一个新对象，但不复制调用对象的数据或索引（仅"
"复制对数据和索引的引用）。对原始数据的任何更改都会反映在浅拷贝中（"
"反之亦然）。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.copy.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.core.Series.copy:13 of
msgid ""
"Make a deep copy, including a copy of the data and the indices. With "
"``deep=False`` neither the indices nor the data are copied."
msgstr ""
"进行深拷贝，包括数据和索引的副本。当 ``deep=False`` 时，既不复制索引也不"
"复制数据。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.copy.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.core.Series.copy:17 of
msgid "**copy** -- Object type matches caller."
msgstr "**copy** -- 对象类型与调用者匹配。"

#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.copy.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

